11 A BILL
12 TO BE ENTITLED
13 AN ACT
14
15 Relating to property taxes; to amend Act 2023-344, 2024
16 Regular Session, now appearing as Section 40-7-2.2, Code of
17 Alabama 1975, to change the cap on real property tax
18 assessments; and to provide for retroactive effect.
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
20 Section 1. Act 2024-344, Regular Session 2024, now
21 appearing as Section 40-7-2.2, Code of Alabama 1975 is amended
22 to read as follows:
23 "§40-7-2.2
